OL,3,CCowboy builder sentenced after loft
OL,4,Cconversion 'could have collapsed'
OL,6,FA cowboy builder who carried out sub-
OL,7,Fstandard work in Swindon, leaving some
OL,8,Funfinished and unsafe, has been
OL,9,Fsentenced.
OL,11,FRaj Kumar Bagga, who's 59 and from
OL,12,FWoodside Avenue, Old Walcot, began
OL,13,Fwork on a loft conversion which a
OL,14,Fsurveyor said could have
OL,15,Fcatastrophically collapsed.
OL,17,FThe judge called Bagga "highly
OL,18,Freckless", causing his victims
OL,19,Fsuffering and misery.
