OL,3,CCowboy builder sentenced after loft
OL,4,Cconversion 'could have collapsed'
OL,6,FThe offences were committed by Bagga
OL,7,Fwhen he was trading under the name of
OL,8,FR and L Building Solutions.
OL,10,FHe was handed an eight month prison
OL,11,Fsentence which was suspended for 18
OL,12,Fmonths.
OL,14,FHe will have to carry out 200 hours of
OL,15,Fcommunity service and he's been given
OL,16,Fa criminal behaviour order,
OL,17,Fprohibiting him from undertaking any
OL,18,Fbuilding work in his own capacity, or
OL,19,Fany business operated by him for 10
OL,20,Fyears.
